    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "Use dice rolls to randomly determine how many villagers are healed with each potion.\r\n\r\n## Do This: \r\n- Run the code to see how villagers are healed with each potion.\r\n- Modify the code so that each potion heals between 2 and 5 villagers.",
